Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.index.schema

Class RawBits

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.index.schema.RawBits
  • class RawBits
extends Object
    Useful to compare values stored as raw bits and value type without having to box them as number values.

    • Method Detail

      • asNumberValue

        static NumberValue asNumberValue​(long rawBits,
                                 byte type)
        Convert value represented by type and raw bits to corresponding NumberValue. If type is not BYTE, SHORT, INT, LONG, FLOAT or DOUBLE, the raw bits will be interpreted as a long.
        Parameters:
        rawBits - Raw bits of value
        type - Type of value
        Returns:
        NumberValue with type and value given by provided raw bits and type.

      • compare

        static int compare​(long lhsRawBits,
                   byte lhsType,
                   long rhsRawBits,
                   byte rhsType)
        Compare number values represented by type and raw bits. If type is not BYTE, SHORT, INT, LONG, FLOAT or DOUBLE, the raw bits will be compared as long.
        Parameters:
        lhsRawBits - Raw bits of left hand side value
        lhsType - Type of left hand side value
        rhsRawBits - Raw bits of right hand side value
        rhsType - Type of right hand side value
        Returns:
        An int less that 0 if lhs value is numerically less than rhs value. An int equal to 0 if lhs and rhs value are numerically equal (independent of type) and an int greater than 0 if lhs value is greater than rhs value.
